  "detailed_description": "<h1>Buzz</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/10e064530ab18e21b6355826328f43d7.avif?t=1671670445\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br><br>Mikaela Cohen, a workaholic junior architect based in Boston, is in for a surprisingly long vacation. While accompanying her boss on a business trip in Aspen, an unexpected blizzard traps the two architects at the ski resort where they are staying. <br><br>What will happen to Mikaela while she awaits the end of the blizzard? <br><br>Who will she meet in this snowy Colorado town? <br><br>Will she learn to balance her life and maybe make time for love? <br><br>Only you can find out by playing “Colorado Cocoa Club”.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/99d667f35b9be783d6a8b2f31f85dc7b.poster.avif?t=1671670445\" width=640 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/99d667f35b9be783d6a8b2f31f85dc7b.webm?t=1671670445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/99d667f35b9be783d6a8b2f31f85dc7b.mp4?t=1671670445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- A charming and hilarious storyline in an alpine setting.<br>- Beautiful Anime influenced character art<br>- Classy Modern Jazz Soundtrack<br>- Multiple endings based on your choices",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/10e064530ab18e21b6355826328f43d7.avif?t=1671670445\" width=640 height=240 /></span><br><br>Mikaela Cohen, a workaholic junior architect based in Boston, is in for a surprisingly long vacation. While accompanying her boss on a business trip in Aspen, an unexpected blizzard traps the two architects at the ski resort where they are staying. <br><br>What will happen to Mikaela while she awaits the end of the blizzard? <br><br>Who will she meet in this snowy Colorado town? <br><br>Will she learn to balance her life and maybe make time for love? <br><br>Only you can find out by playing “Colorado Cocoa Club”.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/99d667f35b9be783d6a8b2f31f85dc7b.poster.avif?t=1671670445\" width=640 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/99d667f35b9be783d6a8b2f31f85dc7b.webm?t=1671670445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592970/extras/99d667f35b9be783d6a8b2f31f85dc7b.mp4?t=1671670445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- A charming and hilarious storyline in an alpine setting.<br>- Beautiful Anime influenced character art<br>- Classy Modern Jazz Soundtrack<br>- Multiple endings based on your choices",
